			<description><![CDATA[<p>
<strong>Role &amp; Responsibilities</strong></p>
<p>
The Sales Coordinator will report to the Sales Manager and assist clients with travel arrangements. This will include assisting clients to choose and research travel destinations as well as booking the accommodation, flights, travel insurance, ferry tickets and other travel needs.</p>
<p>
The Sales Coordinator will also be required to assist the Sales Manager in finalizing corporate proposals, prepare for sales calls, schedule meetings, and reply to reservation and customer service emails and calls.</p>
<p>
The Sales Coordinator must be fluent in English, comfortable with sales, possess a good working knowledge of Microsoft Office, be proficient at using social networking sites, and possess confidence a strong eye for detail.</p>
<p>
<strong>Requirements</strong></p>
<p>
Diploma and above. Fresh graduates are welcome to apply.<br />
A candidate must have a Journeyful account to be considered.</p>
<p>
&nbsp;</p>
